{"tid":2288271,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"原來安全套一啲都唔安全","createTime":"2020-11-16T11:19:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-12T10:06:32.000Z","uid":376170,"like":33,"dislike":1093,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"da23e2eee3b8862bea1befa388d0f2bac6e8578d","tid":2288271,"uid":376170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:19:43.000Z","msg":"本身有男朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前用交友app識咗條仔，諗住識吓人咁<br />\n<br />\n點知越傾越啱key<br />\n<br />\n冇同男朋友提過亦唔敢提<br />\n<br />\n之後條仔都有一直約我一齊出街睇戲食吓飯咁<br />\n<br />\n大家都覺得大家好夾，我都冇同佢講過我有男朋友<br />\n<br />\n幾個月之後我就約佢上嚟我屋企，因為記得嗰日男朋友有嘢做所以唔會上嚟<br />\n<br />\n之後就扑野啦<br />\n<br />\n點知男朋友突然上嚟攞嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢見到之後就好撚嬲，即刻攞碌棍扑穿咗條仔頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明佢戴左安全套，就應該可以好安全咁扑野<br />\n<br />\n但係佢最後都係比人仆穿咗個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲要爆曬缸<br />\n<br />\ndklm安全套一啲都唔安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb4719b519ab86fab756578e93776beda2881cd","tid":2288271,"uid":308615,"like":50,"dislike":7,"score":43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:20:37.000Z","msg":"一腳踏兩船正仆街黎"},{"pid":"79b7d72f4071b0cb54c548b2c6b5d6c4c6fc219d","tid":2288271,"uid":241764,"like":186,"dislike":3,"score":183,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:20:49.000Z","msg":"好尷尬"},{"pid":"4ccc839dbe540e8a7c823be03fcffe862da150f8","tid":2288271,"uid":379652,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:21:41.000Z","msg":"唔好咁傻啦"},{"pid":"3c78f09d175e67a2c8f15bcbd948424d25158532","tid":2288271,"uid":198241,"like":63,"dislike":0,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"都係吉屎忽<br />\n叫埋男朋友一齊吉咪得<br />\n點解要用碌野扑人個頭??"},{"pid":"f028f7c1933df8e188310afa9295c27